---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import NewsletterSignup from '../../components/NewsletterSignup.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Files from the Parent Coach Desk"
  description="Files, templates, spreadsheets, and cheat sheets for parents who coach. Everything you can take, in one place."
>
  <section class="border-b border-bone">
    <div class="container-px py-16 md:py-20">
      <p class="font-display italic text-rust mb-4 font-medium">Files</p>
      <h1 class="font-display text-ink text-[2.5rem] md:text-[4rem] leading-[1.0] max-w-3xl font-medium">
        Everything you can <em class="text-rust">take with you</em>.
      </h1>
      <p class="font-display text-ink-soft text-xl mt-6 max-w-2xl leading-snug">
        Files from the Parent Coach Desk. Printable PDFs, templates, and cheat sheets organized by what you need. Some you grab in 5 seconds. Some are full how-to articles. None gated behind anything fancier than your email.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FREE DOWNLOADS (PDFs) -->
  <section class="border-b border-bone">
    <div class="container-px py-12">
      <p class="font-display italic text-rust mb-2 font-medium" style="font-size: 1.05rem">Files you can grab</p>
      <p class="font-display text-ink-soft mb-6 leading-snug max-w-2xl">
        Printable files straight from the Desk. Subscribe once and they're yours. New files added when we ship them.
      </p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-px bg-bone">

        <a href="/resources/what-to-say-when/" class="bg-paper p-7 group block hover:bg-paper-warm transition-colors">
          <p class="font-display italic text-rust mb-2 text-sm font-medium">PDF · 28 pages</p>
          <h3 class="font-display text-ink text-2xl leading-tight group-hover:text-rust transition-colors font-medium">
            What to Say When
          </h3>
          <p class="font-display text-ink-soft mt-3 leading-snug text-sm">
            A field guide for sports parents. Twenty-three scripts for before, after, and the hard moments in between. By age. Plus a tri-fold pocket card.
          </p>
          <div class="t-cta mt-4">Send me the field guide →</div>
        </a>

        <a href="/resources/practice-plan-template/" class="bg-paper p-7 group block hover:bg-paper-warm transition-colors">
          <p class="font-display italic text-rust mb-2 text-sm font-medium">PDF · 4 pages</p>
          <h3 class="font-display text-ink text-2xl leading-tight group-hover:text-rust transition-colors font-medium">
            The Practice Plan Template
          </h3>
          <p class="font-display text-ink-soft mt-3 leading-snug text-sm">
            A printable practice plan parents can read. Blank template, filled example, drill ideas by age band.
          </p>
          <div class="t-cta mt-4">Send me the template →</div>
        </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TEMPLATES & SPREADSHEETS (link to Team Parent) -->
  <section class="border-b border-bone">
    <div class="container-px py-12">
      <p class="font-display italic text-rust mb-2 font-medium" style="font-size: 1.05rem">Templates and walkthroughs</p>
      <p class="font-display text-ink-soft mb-6 leading-snug max-w-2xl">
        Spreadsheets, Google Docs, and step-by-step setups. Live inside the Team Parent toolkit.
      </p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <a href="/team-parent/fair-lineup-spreadsheet/" class="block border border-bone p-5 bg-paper hover:bg-paper-warm transition-colors group">
          <div class="font-display italic text-rust text-xs mb-1 font-medium">Spreadsheet</div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-ink text-lg leading-tight group-hover:text-rust transition-colors font-medium">The fair lineup spreadsheet</h3>
          <p class="font-display text-ink-soft text-sm mt-2 leading-snug">Inning-by-inning rotation that's actually fair.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/team-parent/practice-plan-parents-can-read/" class="block border border-bone p-5 bg-paper hover:bg-paper-warm transition-colors group">
          <div class="font-display italic text-rust text-xs mb-1 font-medium">Google Doc setup</div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-ink text-lg leading-tight group-hover:text-rust transition-colors font-medium">A practice plan parents can read</h3>
          <p class="font-display text-ink-soft text-sm mt-2 leading-snug">10 minutes a week of writing saves 10 phone calls.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/team-parent/setting-up-gamechanger/" class="block border border-bone p-5 bg-paper hover:bg-paper-warm transition-colors group">
          <div class="font-display italic text-rust text-xs mb-1 font-medium">Walkthrough</div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-ink text-lg leading-tight group-hover:text-rust transition-colors font-medium">Setting up GameChanger</h3>
          <p class="font-display text-ink-soft text-sm mt-2 leading-snug">The 20-minute setup that turns one team mom into the league hero.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/team-parent/starting-the-team-group-chat/" class="block border border-bone p-5 bg-paper hover:bg-paper-warm transition-colors group">
          <div class="font-display italic text-rust text-xs mb-1 font-medium">Script + rules</div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-ink text-lg leading-tight group-hover:text-rust transition-colors font-medium">Starting the team group chat</h3>
          <p class="font-display text-ink-soft text-sm mt-2 leading-snug">The first message that works, and five rules to keep it tight.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/team-parent/travel-tournament-packing-list/" class="block border border-bone p-5 bg-paper hover:bg-paper-warm transition-colors group">
          <div class="font-display italic text-rust text-xs mb-1 font-medium">Checklist</div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-ink text-lg leading-tight group-hover:text-rust transition-colors font-medium">Travel-tournament packing list</h3>
          <p class="font-display text-ink-soft text-sm mt-2 leading-snug">What to bring to a Saturday-Sunday tournament. Tape it inside the bag.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/team-parent/recruit-assistant-coaches/" class="block border border-bone p-5 bg-paper hover:bg-paper-warm transition-colors group">
          <div class="font-display italic text-rust text-xs mb-1 font-medium">Script</div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-ink text-lg leading-tight group-hover:text-rust transition-colors font-medium">How to recruit assistant coaches</h3>
          <p class="font-display text-ink-soft text-sm mt-2 leading-snug">The text message that gets two of three parents to say yes.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-6">
        <a href="/team-parent/" class="t-cta">See the full Team Parent toolkit →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CHEAT SHEETS BY SITUATION -->
  <section class="border-b border-bone">
    <div class="container-px py-12">
      <p class="font-display italic text-rust mb-2 font-medium" style="font-size: 1.05rem">Cheat sheets by situation</p>
      <p class="font-display text-ink-soft mb-6 leading-snug max-w-2xl">
        Short reads with the rule, the script, or the move you need in five minutes.
      </p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <a href="/drive-home/the-90-second-rule/" class="block border-l-2 border-rust pl-4 py-3 hover:bg-paper-warm transition-colors group">
          <h3 class="font-display text-ink text-lg leading-tight group-hover:text-rust transition-colors font-medium">The 90-second rule</h3>
          <p class="font-display text-ink-soft text-sm mt-1 leading-snug">What to say in the first 90 seconds after a game.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/drive-there/night-before-tryouts/" class="block border-l-2 border-rust pl-4 py-3 hover:bg-paper-warm transition-colors group">
          <h3 class="font-display text-ink text-lg leading-tight group-hover:text-rust transition-colors font-medium">The night before tryouts</h3>
          <p class="font-display text-ink-soft text-sm mt-1 leading-snug">What to do, what not to ask.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/team-parent/t-ball-cones-stop-the-bunching/" class="block border-l-2 border-rust pl-4 py-3 hover:bg-paper-warm transition-colors group">
          <h3 class="font-display text-ink text-lg leading-tight group-hover:text-rust transition-colors font-medium">T-ball cones</h3>
          <p class="font-display text-ink-soft text-sm mt-1 leading-snug">Five cones, ten minutes of setup, zero bunching.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/drive-home/on-not-making-varsity/" class="block border-l-2 border-rust pl-4 py-3 hover:bg-paper-warm transition-colors group">
          <h3 class="font-display text-ink text-lg leading-tight group-hover:text-rust transition-colors font-medium">On not making varsity</h3>
          <p class="font-display text-ink-soft text-sm mt-1 leading-snug">Sixteen words. The whole job, in three sentences.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/drive-there/the-pre-game-conversation-isnt-strategy/" class="block border-l-2 border-rust pl-4 py-3 hover:bg-paper-warm transition-colors group">
          <h3 class="font-display text-ink text-lg leading-tight group-hover:text-rust transition-colors font-medium">The drive there isn't strategy hour</h3>
          <p class="font-display text-ink-soft text-sm mt-1 leading-snug">Three things to say in 12 minutes. Then stop.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/team-parent/picture-day-pro-or-parent/" class="block border-l-2 border-rust pl-4 py-3 hover:bg-paper-warm transition-colors group">
          <h3 class="font-display text-ink text-lg leading-tight group-hover:text-rust transition-colors font-medium">Picture day decisions</h3>
          <p class="font-display text-ink-soft text-sm mt-1 leading-snug">Pro photographer or just one parent? An honest take.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- COMING NEXT -->
  <section class="border-b border-bone bg-paper-warm">
    <div class="container-px py-10">
      <p class="font-display italic text-rust mb-3 font-medium" style="font-size: 1.05rem">In the works</p>
      <ul class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-y-2 gap-x-8 font-display text-ink-soft">
        <li>The Tryouts Evaluation Rubric (PDF, 1 page)</li>
        <li>The Season-Opener Parent Meeting Agenda (script + handout)</li>
        <li>The Pre-Game Pocket Card (laminate-able, glove-box-sized)</li>
        <li>The Snack Signup Google Form template</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="font-display italic text-ink-soft text-sm mt-4 font-medium">
        Subscribe and you'll be the first to grab them.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- NATIONAL ORGANIZATIONS -->
  <section class="border-b border-bone">
    <div class="container-px py-12">
      <p class="font-display italic text-rust mb-2 font-medium" style="font-size: 1.05rem">National organizations</p>
      <p class="font-display text-ink-soft mb-4 leading-snug max-w-2xl">
        The authoritative bodies behind the rules, certifications, and research we cite throughout the site. Not competitors. Sources we credit.
      </p>
      <a href="/resources/national-organizations/" class="t-cta">See the full directory →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <NewsletterSignup
    headline="Get every download we ship"
    blurb="One subscribe, every current and future free download. One short read a week. Easy unsubscribe."
    buttonLabel="Subscribe"
  />
</BaseLayout>
